&amp;cauthor_uid=18366252">Rafael Mikolajczyk</a></div></div><div id="_co_idm139826160750304"><h3 class="no_margin">Marco Massari</h3><p><sup>8</sup> Istituto Superiore di Sanit&#x000e0;, Rome, Italy </p><div>Find articles by <a href="/pubmed/?term=Massari%20M%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=18366252">Marco Massari</a></div></div><div id="_co_idm139826160748080"><h3 class="no_margin">Stefania Salmaso</h3><p><sup>8</sup> Istituto Superiore di Sanit&#x000e0;, Rome, Italy </p><div>Find articles by <a href="/pubmed/?term=Salmaso%20S%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=18366252">Stefania Salmaso</a></div></div><div id="_co_idm139826235564944"><h3 class="no_margin">Gianpaolo Scalia Tomba</h3><p><sup>9</sup> Department of Mathematics, University of Rome Tor Vergata, Rome, Italy </p><div>Find articles by <a href="/pubmed/?term=Tomba%20GS%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=18366252">Gianpaolo Scalia Tomba</a></div></div><div id="_co_idm139826158265456"><h3 class="no_margin">Jacco Wallinga</h3><p><sup>10</sup> Centre for Infectious Disease Control Netherlands, National Institute for Public Health and the Environment, Bilthoven, The Netherlands </p><div>Find articles by <a href="/pubmed/?term=Wallinga%20J%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=18366252">Jacco Wallinga</a></div></div><div id="_co_idm139826161130496"><h3 class="no_margin">Janneke Heijne</h3><p><sup>10</sup> Centre for Infectious Disease Control Netherlands, National Institute for Public Health and the Environment, Bilthoven, The Netherlands </p><div>Find articles by <a href="/pubmed/?term=Heijne%20J%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=18366252">Janneke Heijne</a></div></div><div id="_co_idm139826159554432"><h3 class="no_margin">Malgorzata Sadkowska-Todys</h3><p><sup>11</sup> National Institute of Hygiene, Warsaw, Poland </p><div>Find articles by <a href="/pubmed/?term=Sadkowska-Todys%20M%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=18366252">Malgorzata Sadkowska-Todys</a></div></div><div id="_co_idm139826159552320"><h3 class="no_margin">Magdalena Rosinska</h3><p><sup>11</sup> National Institute of Hygiene, Warsaw, Poland </p><div>Find articles by <a href="/pubmed/?term=Rosinska%20M%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=18366252">Magdalena Rosinska</a></div></div><div id="_co_idm139826159847136"><h3 class="no_margin">W. John Edmunds</h3><p><sup>4</sup> Modelling and Economics Unit, Health Protection Agency Centre for Infections, London, United Kingdom </p><div>Find articles by <a href="/pubmed/?term=Edmunds%20WJ%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=18366252">W. John Edmunds</a></div></div></div></div><div class="contrib-group half_rhythm fm-editor">Steven Riley, <span class="fm-role">Academic Editor</span><sup></sup></div><div class="fm-panel half_rhythm"><div class="togglers"><a href="#" class="pmctoggle" rid="idm139826202622736_ai idm139826164460704_ai idm139826159654160_ai">Author information</a> <a href="#" class="pmctoggle" rid="idm139826202622736_an">Article notes</a> <a href="#" class="pmctoggle" rid="idm139826202622736_cpl">Copyright and License information</a> <a href="/pmc/about/disclaimer/">Disclaimer</a></div><div class="fm-authors-info fm-panel hide half_rhythm" id="idm139826202622736_ai" style="display:none"><div class="fm-affl" lang="en" id="aff1"><sup>1</sup> Microbiology Unit, Laboratoire National de Sant&#x000e9;, Luxembourg, Luxembourg </div><div class="fm-affl" lang="en" id="aff2"><sup>2</sup> Centre de Recherche Public Sant&#x000e9;, Luxembourg, Luxembourg </div><div class="fm-affl" lang="en" id="aff3"><sup>3</sup> Center for Statistics, Hasselt University, Diepenbeek, Belgium </div><div class="fm-affl" lang="en" id="aff4"><sup>4</sup> Modelling and Economics Unit, Health Protection Agency Centre for Infections, London, United Kingdom </div><div class="fm-affl" lang="en" id="aff5"><sup>5</sup> Unit Health Economic and Modeling Infectious Diseases, Center for the Evaluation of Vaccination, Vac